Detailed Description

cvmx_osm_int_info_addr

This register can be used to debug address errors (illegal bank). Fields are captured when there are no outstanding address errors indicated in OSM_INT_STAT and a new address error arrives. Prioritization for multiple events occurring at the same time is indicated by the OSM_ADDR_ERR_SOURCE_E enumeration; highest encoded value has highest priority.
